Double Punch/Manterror/Injector/Bumblebee:



Bumblebee threw down his glass of liquid energon, taking out both of his 
stinger missile launchers, feeling the base shake lightly.  He charged for 
the nearest entry hatch.

---

Double Punch fell, shots hitting the ship.  He got up quickly, running for 
the nearest access hatch.

---

Manterror stormed out of his quarters with Injector, both heading for the 
nearest access hatch.

---
 
Manterror and Injector spotted Mosquitor run off like an idiot, than spotted 
GoldenEye.

Both raised their weapons.

"Who are you?" Manterror asked, getting ready to fire.
